OL,3,CDate set for Caerphilly by-election
OL,4,Cfollowing death of Hefin David
OL,6,FA date for a by-election to fill the
OL,7,Fseat of late Senedd Member Hefin David
OL,8,Fhas been announced following his death
OL,9,Flast month.
OL,11,FMr David died suddenly on August 12
OL,12,Faged 47. He had been a Member of the
OL,13,FSenedd for Labour in Caerphilly since
OL,14,F2016 and re-elected in 2021.
OL,16,FThe Senedd's Llywydd has now declared
OL,17,Fthat a by-election will take place in
OL,18,Fthe constituency on October 23.
