OL,3,CDate set for Caerphilly by-election
OL,4,Cfollowing death of Hefin David
OL,6,FIn a statement to the Welsh
OL,7,FParliament, Llywydd Elin Jones said:
OL,8,F"I have announced that the Caerphilly
OL,9,Fby-election will take place on 23
OL,10,FOctober 2025 and have written to the
OL,11,FReturning Officer asking him to
OL,12,Farrange for the poll to take place on
OL,13,Fthat date."
OL,15,FA by-election must be held within
OL,16,Fthree months of a seat being declared
OL,17,Fvacant which would make Tuesday,
OL,18,FNovember 11, the last possible date.
