OL,3,CDate set for Caerphilly by-election
OL,4,Cfollowing death of Hefin David
OL,6,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,7,Fmedical emergency at an address in
OL,8,FNelson area of Caerphilly at around
OL,9,F6.55pm on 12 August.
OL,11,FGwent Police previously said
OL,12,Fparamedics attended and confirmed that
OL,13,Fthe man had died. Mr David was
OL,14,Fidentified at the scene by his sister.
OL,16,FAn inquest into the serving
OL,17,Fpolitician's death has been opened and
OL,18,Fadjourned, to be held in April next
OL,19,Fyear.
