OL,3,CDate set for Caerphilly by-election
OL,4,Cfollowing death of Hefin David
OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan was among
OL,7,Fthose who attended the funeral on
OL,8,FMonday (1 September) of the Labour
OL,9,Fpolitician.
OL,11,FMr David's family described him as a
OL,12,F"devoted father" and "soulmate" to his
OL,13,Fpartner Vikki Howells - who is the MS
OL,14,Ffor Cynon Valley and minister for
OL,15,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,16,FWelsh Government.
