OL,3,CDate set for Caerphilly by-election
OL,4,Cfollowing death of Hefin David
OL,6,FIn a tribute previously shared by
OL,7,FWelsh Labour, Mr David's family said:
OL,8,F"It is clear from the very many
OL,9,Fmessages we have received that Hefin
OL,10,Fwas widely respected and held in
OL,11,Fgenuine affection by the community he
OL,12,Frepresented, and by those he worked
OL,13,Fwith during his many years of public
OL,14,Fservice.
