OL,6,F"But more than this, Hefin was a
OL,7,Fdevoted father who was adored by his
OL,8,Fdaughters Caitlin and Holly, a much-
OL,9,Floved son to Wynne and Christine, a
OL,10,Fbeloved brother to Sian, a brilliant
OL,11,Funcle to Osian and Catrin, and a
OL,12,Fsoulmate to his cherished partner
OL,13,FVikki.
OL,15,F"We are very grateful to all those who
OL,16,Fhave reached out to us since Hefin's
OL,17,Fpassing, and ask now for privacy to
OL,18,Fgrieve."
